---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const today = "10 December 2025";
---

<Layout>
    <div class="page-container">
        <h1>Cancellation & Refund Policy</h1>
        <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> {today}</p>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>1. Subscription Cancellation</h2>
            <p>
                MISKILLS subscriptions cannot be manually cancelled by the user
                before the end of the purchased period. Once a subscription is
                purchased, it will remain active until the end of its validity
                period and will then automatically expire unless the user
                chooses to renew. Users may stop using the service at any time,
                but no partial or prorated refunds will be issued for unused
                time.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>2. Refund Eligibility</h2>
            <p>
                MISKILLS provides instant access to digital learning content,
                therefore subscription payments are generally non-refundable.
            </p>
            <p>
                Refunds may be issued only in special cases such as duplicate
                payments or failed transactions.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>3. Refund Processing</h2>
            <p>
                Approved refunds will be processed to the original payment
                method within 5–7 business days as per Razorpay’s settlement
                timelines.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .page-container {
        max-width: 768px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 4rem 1rem;
        font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif;
        color: #111;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    p,
    li {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.75rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: #444;
    }

    ul {
        padding-left: 1.25rem;
    }

    strong {
        color: #000;
    }

    .section {
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
</style>
